Package se.arkalix.core.plugin

Arrowhead Kalix Core Service Plugins

This package contains various plugins useful for interacting with the Arrowhead Framework core services.

Currently, the most significant component of this package is the HttpJsonCoreIntegrator class.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ArOrchestration
    Represents an Arrowhead orchestration service.
    ArServiceDiscovery
    Represents an Arrowhead service discovery service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HttpJsonCoreIntegrator
    HTTP/JSON core integration plug-in.
    HttpJsonCoreIntegrator.Builder
    Builder useful for constructing HttpJsonCoreIntegrator instances.
    HttpJsonOrchestration
    A remote ArOrchestration service that is communicated with via HTTP/JSON in either secure or insecure mode.
    HttpJsonServiceDiscovery
    A remote ArServiceDiscovery service that is communicated with via HTTP/JSON in either secure or insecure mode.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ArOrchestrationStrategy
    Enumerates the different kind of strategies that can be used when querying an orchestration service for services to consume.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ArCoreIntegrationException
    Signifies the failure to complete a core integration task.
